1
00:00:09,220 --> 00:00:12,050
Phoon, nak tinggal sekali dengan aku?

2
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,973
P'Fah, takkan bosan dengan aku, kan?

3
00:00:15,071 --> 00:00:16,011
Tak mungkin.

4
00:00:16,084 --> 00:00:18,250
Nak jumpa ibu kau?

5
00:00:18,737 --> 00:00:20,988
Kau kata kau akan bawa aku ke mana saja.

6
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:23,114
Aku dah tahu nak pergi mana.

7
00:00:23,688 --> 00:00:25,591
P'Fah, boleh kita balik sekarang?

8
00:00:26,010 --> 00:00:28,968
- Kenapa?
- Aku tak sangka sejuk macam ni.

9
00:00:29,306 --> 00:00:30,720
Tolong aku cari ibu Phoon.

10
00:00:31,589 --> 00:00:32,487
Ibu kandung dia.

11
00:00:32,717 --> 00:00:34,712
Boleh tak berhenti campur tangan hidup Phoon?

12
00:00:34,951 --> 00:00:36,654
Dia dah cukup banyak bertahan.

13
00:00:36,902 --> 00:00:38,294
Tolong lepaskan dia.

14
00:00:42,714 --> 00:00:45,053
Terima kasih, P'Fah, tolong aku cari ibu aku.

15
00:00:48,567 --> 00:00:49,677
Tak ada apa-apa.

16
00:00:56,090 --> 00:00:57,802
Separuh Jepun.

17
00:00:59,253 --> 00:01:03,522
Dia ada seorang anak dan sekarang umur 39.

18
00:01:04,922 --> 00:01:08,837
Jadi dia mesti dapat aku masa umur 19.

19
00:01:12,691 --> 00:01:13,774
P'Fah.

20
00:01:14,808 --> 00:01:15,417
Ya?

21
00:01:15,798 --> 00:01:17,789
Mesti dia belum bersedia masa dapat aku.

22
00:01:21,494 --> 00:01:23,162
Bersedia atau tak, aku tak tahu.

23
00:01:23,829 --> 00:01:26,554
Tapi dia hantar hadiah tiap tahun, kan?

24
00:01:28,045 --> 00:01:29,312
Lagipun,

25
00:01:30,262 --> 00:01:32,383
nama kau dan nama ibu kau dalam Jepun,

26
00:01:33,728 --> 00:01:35,592
dua-dua maksudnya bunga.

27
00:01:37,127 --> 00:01:38,351
Macam mana?

28
00:01:39,888 --> 00:01:40,865
Yuri.

29
00:01:41,241 --> 00:01:42,481
Maksudnya lili.

30
00:01:43,115 --> 00:01:44,739
Dan Ren maksudnya teratai.

31
00:01:52,717 --> 00:01:54,336
Kau nak jumpa ibu kau?

32
00:01:57,345 --> 00:01:58,342
Aku tak pasti.

33
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,154
Dia dah ada keluarga baharu.

34
00:02:01,678 --> 00:02:03,417
Kalau aku jumpa dia, aku takut

35
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:07,368
aku rosakkan hidup baharu yang dia bina.

36
00:02:09,699 --> 00:02:12,994
Jadi kenapa tak cuba hubungi dia dulu?

37
00:02:14,072 --> 00:02:17,222
Kalau dia tak selesa, kau boleh undur.

38
00:02:21,247 --> 00:02:23,305
Aku buat kau rasa tak selesa ke?

39
00:02:24,589 --> 00:02:25,835
Kau tak perlu fikir sangat.

40
00:02:26,970 --> 00:02:28,373
Kalau kau tak nak pergi, tak apa.

41
00:02:31,979 --> 00:02:33,194
Sebenarnya,

42
00:02:34,371 --> 00:02:35,979
aku memang nak jumpa dia sekurang-kurangnya sekali.

43
00:02:47,457 --> 00:02:48,917
Nama anak dia Daiki.

44
00:02:50,143 --> 00:02:51,460
Aku akan ada adik.

45
00:02:52,557 --> 00:02:53,585
Comelnya.

46
00:04:32,598 --> 00:04:34,242
Maew, kau kacukan ke?

47
00:04:35,623 --> 00:04:36,680
Tak juga.

48
00:04:38,536 --> 00:04:40,614
Mak aku yang kacukan.

49
00:04:41,610 --> 00:04:44,841
Oh, jadi kau 25% Jepun?

50
00:04:46,788 --> 00:04:49,630
Separuh ikut mak kau, kan?

51
00:04:51,499 --> 00:04:52,376
Jadi?

52
00:04:53,022 --> 00:04:54,397
Kau nak jumpa dia ke?

53
00:04:56,155 --> 00:04:57,241
Aku tak tahu.

54
00:04:57,795 --> 00:04:59,245
Ibu aku dah ada keluarga baharu.

55
00:05:00,051 --> 00:05:01,460
Aku tak tahu

56
00:05:02,143 --> 00:05:03,700
patut pergi atau tak.

57
00:05:06,994 --> 00:05:08,167
Aku rasa kau patut.

58
00:05:08,955 --> 00:05:10,611
Mungkin dia rindu kau sangat.

59
00:05:11,161 --> 00:05:13,223
Kalau tak, kenapa dia hantar hadiah?

60
00:05:13,367 --> 00:05:14,442
Ya, betul juga.

61
00:05:16,146 --> 00:05:17,477
Kenapa tak cuba hubungi dia dulu?

62
00:05:18,771 --> 00:05:19,922
Macam hantar surat.

63
00:05:24,549 --> 00:05:25,031
Hmm,

64
00:05:25,777 --> 00:05:26,660
itu boleh jadi.

65
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,632
Aku akan tulis surat pada dia dulu.

66
00:05:28,811 --> 00:05:30,484
Kalau dia tak balas, nanti aku hadap saja.

67
00:05:31,352 --> 00:05:32,933
Dia akan balas.

68
00:05:35,171 --> 00:05:36,527
Apa-apa pun, tahniah.

69
00:05:37,053 --> 00:05:40,465
Akhirnya kau tahu siapa ibu kau.

70
00:05:41,257 --> 00:05:41,826
Ya.

71
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,764
Macam mana dengan ayah kau?

72
00:05:51,902 --> 00:05:53,355
Rasanya dah tamat.

73
00:05:54,074 --> 00:05:55,792
Dia dah terima akibat atas apa dia buat.

74
00:05:56,573 --> 00:05:58,118
Aku akan hidup cara aku.

75
00:05:58,844 --> 00:06:00,927
Hidup berasingan macam ni pun tak apa.

76
00:06:06,721 --> 00:06:08,262
Aku bangga sangat dengan kau.

77
00:06:08,949 --> 00:06:12,617
Kau dah banyak berubah. Betul-betul matang.

78
00:06:12,948 --> 00:06:16,274
- Dulu kau menangis bila ayah kau disebut.
- Betul.

79
00:06:16,663 --> 00:06:20,585
- Kau memang hebat.
- Bila dia cakap pasal ayah dia, muka dia kelakar sangat.

80
00:06:23,816 --> 00:06:25,108
Apa masalah kau?

81
00:06:27,814 --> 00:06:28,951
Padan muka.

82
00:06:29,327 --> 00:06:30,327
Hah, mula dah.

83
00:06:30,733 --> 00:06:31,617
Terima kasih.

84
00:06:33,088 --> 00:06:34,721
Masa aku paling teruk,

85
00:06:34,885 --> 00:06:35,939
koranglah satu-satunya

86
00:06:36,426 --> 00:06:37,448
yang buat semuanya jadi lebih baik.

87
00:06:40,905 --> 00:06:42,395
Aku ni orang yang tak bernasib baik.

88
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,038
Semua nasib baik aku habis

89
00:06:45,447 --> 00:06:47,299
sebab jumpa kawan baik macam korang.

90
00:06:51,949 --> 00:06:56,005
- Maew, berhenti, dia nak menangis dah.
- Aku tak menangis. Kau yang menangis. Jangan lebih.

91
00:06:56,315 --> 00:06:58,314
Kau sengguk-sengguk.

92
00:06:58,994 --> 00:07:01,442
Maew, betul, tak ada apa-apa pun.

93
00:07:01,783 --> 00:07:03,414
Kau tak perlu berterima kasih.

94
00:07:04,437 --> 00:07:05,896
Belanja minum kami sudah.

95
00:07:09,321 --> 00:07:11,022
Serius.

96
00:07:11,324 --> 00:07:14,928
Kau langsung tak peka, tak pandai baca suasana.

97
00:07:17,065 --> 00:07:19,025
Aku cuma tak suka suasana macam ni.

98
00:07:19,225 --> 00:07:20,379
Terlalu tegang.

99
00:07:25,515 --> 00:07:26,727
Wei.

100
00:07:29,954 --> 00:07:30,866
Terima kasih.

101
00:07:32,811 --> 00:07:33,554
Kau cakap apa ni?

102
00:07:35,675 --> 00:07:38,257
Terima kasih sebab tolong aku dalam semua hal.

103
00:07:38,648 --> 00:07:40,401
Termasuk masa Phoon ada masalah.

104
00:07:41,222 --> 00:07:42,194
Kau sedar tak?

105
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:45,980
- Kau macam hero kumpulan.
- Hero konon.

106
00:07:46,629 --> 00:07:50,390
- Kau gila? Tiba-tiba je ucap terima kasih.
- North dah merah muka.

107
00:07:50,837 --> 00:07:52,143
Aku serius.

108
00:07:53,216 --> 00:07:55,080
Aku gembira sangat ada kawan macam kau.

109
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:57,549
Ada kawan macam kau dalam hidup ni

110
00:08:00,096 --> 00:08:01,656
lagi berbaloi daripada menang loteri.

111
00:08:05,247 --> 00:08:06,225
Aku sayang kau sangat.

112
00:08:07,268 --> 00:08:09,555
Wei, apa cerita ayat sayang-sayang ni?

113
00:08:10,290 --> 00:08:12,712
Kau gila ke, Ter? Apa kau merepek ni?

114
00:08:12,771 --> 00:08:15,524
- Taklah.
- Buat cool, tapi merah muka, kan?

115
00:08:16,097 --> 00:08:18,851
- Taklah.
- Kau memang merah muka.

116
00:08:18,902 --> 00:08:20,733
- Aku nampak.
- Kau ni gila? Cukup.

117
00:08:20,783 --> 00:08:24,349
Ramai orang kat sini. Kau buat apa ni?

118
00:08:25,696 --> 00:08:26,930
Tapi betul,

119
00:08:29,330 --> 00:08:30,349
aku memang gembira

120
00:08:30,681 --> 00:08:31,722
dapat kau jadi kawan aku.

121
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:37,641
Kau tahu tak kau selalu bagi semangat pada kami?

122
00:08:42,677 --> 00:08:43,591
Sayang kau, bro.

123
00:08:44,044 --> 00:08:46,048
Wei, berhenti dengan benda sayang-sayang ni. Tak.

124
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:49,103
- Cakap kau sayang kami.
- Apa merepek sayang lagi ni?

125
00:08:49,130 --> 00:08:52,251
- Tadi aku terbawa perasaan.
- Terbawa perasaan pasal apa?

126
00:08:52,487 --> 00:08:55,305
- Cepatlah.
- Ter, jaga perangai.

127
00:08:55,794 --> 00:08:56,755
Kau gila ke?

128
00:08:57,955 --> 00:08:58,703
Dia cuma malu.

129
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,460
Dah tiga orang siap.

130
00:09:09,897 --> 00:09:12,706
Tak, aku tak nak cakap.

131
00:09:12,921 --> 00:09:13,602
Wei.

132
00:09:20,931 --> 00:09:24,063
- Terima kasih, Dao.
- Terima kasih banyak, Dao.

133
00:09:24,235 --> 00:09:26,256
Dao bagi nasihat yang memang bagus.

134
00:09:26,337 --> 00:09:29,059
- Kalau tak ada kau.
- Serius, kumpulan ni dah berpecah.

135
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,435
Tanpa Dao, memang hancur.

136
00:09:31,465 --> 00:09:33,093
Aku gembira sangat.

137
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,087
Walaupun kau tak pernah makan dengan kami.

138
00:09:47,310 --> 00:09:50,143
Kepada Cik Nakamura Yuri.

139
00:09:55,093 --> 00:09:57,324
Hai, nama saya Typhoon.

140
00:09:57,410 --> 00:10:01,642
Saya anak puan. Boleh saya panggil puan Ibu?

141
00:10:02,124 --> 00:10:06,371
Saya tak tahu sama ada wajar saya tulis pada puan.

142
00:10:07,272 --> 00:10:12,722
Tapi saya nak puan tahu saya gembira dapat tahu ibu kandung saya.

143
00:10:12,986 --> 00:10:18,102
Baru-baru ini saya tahu ada orang hantar hadiah hari jadi tiap tahun.

144
00:10:19,365 --> 00:10:24,454
Kalau itu puan, saya gembira puan masih ingat saya.

145
00:10:38,164 --> 00:10:41,349
Saya tak marah puan tak ada dengan saya.

146
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:47,619
Apa pun sebabnya, saya cuma harap puan sihat dan baik.

147
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,600
Bagi aku, aku baik-baik saja.

148
00:11:31,315 --> 00:11:34,453
Aku dah jumpa orang yang aku sayang, dan sayang aku.

149
00:11:37,368 --> 00:11:38,499
Terima kasih.

150
00:11:38,696 --> 00:11:40,720
Boleh aku upah awak gayakan aku seumur hidup?

151
00:11:40,971 --> 00:11:43,518
Boleh, tapi

152
00:11:43,934 --> 00:11:44,985
ada bayaran sikit.

153
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,634
Mahal ke?

154
00:11:49,546 --> 00:11:51,954
Tak langsung. Cuma...

155
00:11:52,983 --> 00:11:53,737
satu ciuman.

156
00:11:58,678 --> 00:12:00,700
Apa awak cakap ni?

157
00:12:01,709 --> 00:12:03,168
Kebelakangan ni awak makin comel.

158
00:12:04,512 --> 00:12:07,074
Bila aku cakap macam tu, awak jadi malu.

159
00:12:08,463 --> 00:12:09,585
Awak comel, P'Fah.

160
00:12:11,838 --> 00:12:13,177
Berhenti.

161
00:12:17,930 --> 00:12:21,250
Aku ada kawan dan orang baik di sekeliling aku.

162
00:12:22,882 --> 00:12:23,761
Hei.

163
00:12:37,266 --> 00:12:38,442
Fakulti Seni Halus.

164
00:12:49,131 --> 00:12:51,930
Aku dah jumpa tujuan dan matlamat hidup aku.

165
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:56,835
Kalau suatu hari Mama tertanya aku okay ke,

166
00:12:57,284 --> 00:12:59,711
aku baik saja. Jangan risau.

167
00:13:00,882 --> 00:13:01,896
Buat yang terbaik, Phoon.

168
00:13:03,262 --> 00:13:03,967
Okey.

169
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:21,829
Aku nak jumpa Mama.

170
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:27,084
Tapi kalau Mama tak nak jumpa aku, tak apa. Aku faham.

171
00:13:27,401 --> 00:13:33,385
Semoga Mama bahagia dan senyum tiap hari. Daripada Typhoon.

172
00:13:33,866 --> 00:13:34,579
Ren.

173
00:14:14,548 --> 00:14:15,269
Ada apa-apa?

174
00:14:16,315 --> 00:14:17,183
Sekejap ya.

175
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:37,900
Mungkin dia tak nak jumpa aku.

176
00:14:38,749 --> 00:14:40,225
Sebab tu dia tak balas.

177
00:14:43,857 --> 00:14:45,250
Jangan buat kesimpulan sendiri.

178
00:14:55,002 --> 00:14:56,774
Lepas ni awak nak buat apa?

179
00:14:57,328 --> 00:14:58,985
Mungkin aku akan cari kerja.

180
00:14:59,162 --> 00:15:01,530
Mulakan hidup baharu dengan Fai, kami berdua saja.

181
00:15:03,377 --> 00:15:04,650
Mesti susah.

182
00:15:05,248 --> 00:15:08,494
Sekurang-kurangnya aku lega, takkan ada yang sakiti kami lagi.

183
00:15:09,194 --> 00:15:10,410
Kau pun, Phoon.

184
00:15:10,638 --> 00:15:12,373
Hiduplah dengan bahagia.

185
00:15:12,702 --> 00:15:14,986
Aku akan bawa Fai datang selalu.

186
00:15:16,004 --> 00:15:16,551
Okey.

187
00:15:16,945 --> 00:15:18,896
Tolong jaga diri baik-baik, Mak Cik Phrae.

188
00:15:41,536 --> 00:15:42,317
Awak dah balik?

189
00:16:24,644 --> 00:16:27,287
Ren, maaf. Mama rindu. Mama akan tunggu.
Daripada Mama

190
00:16:31,248 --> 00:16:32,328
Bagusnya.

191
00:16:37,210 --> 00:16:37,761
Ya.

192
00:16:47,734 --> 00:16:49,554
Selamat menikmati manisan.

193
00:16:56,551 --> 00:16:58,419
Maksudnya apa?

194
00:17:00,235 --> 00:17:02,687
Maksudnya “Selamat menikmati manisan.”

195
00:17:17,419 --> 00:17:18,518
Aku akan

196
00:17:19,031 --> 00:17:20,367
bawa awak jumpa mama awak.

197
00:17:23,008 --> 00:17:24,242
Awak baik sangat.

198
00:17:24,948 --> 00:17:26,983
Hah? Aku?

199
00:17:28,016 --> 00:17:28,555
Ya.

200
00:17:29,785 --> 00:17:31,653
Awak mesti selalu dipuji, kan?

201
00:17:33,677 --> 00:17:34,914
Tak juga.

202
00:17:35,362 --> 00:17:37,072
Dengan orang lain, biasa saja.

203
00:17:37,899 --> 00:17:38,872
Tapi dengan awak...

204
00:17:41,605 --> 00:17:43,680
aku betul-betul sanggup buat apa saja untuk awak.

205
00:17:49,290 --> 00:17:51,797
Tak sabar nak tengok rupa manisan tu.

206
00:17:53,470 --> 00:17:54,266
Macam mana nak buka?

207
00:17:55,333 --> 00:17:56,019
Nah.

208
00:18:05,706 --> 00:18:08,050
Ini dipanggil Manju.

209
00:18:15,001 --> 00:18:16,228
P'Fah nak cuba tak?

210
00:18:16,709 --> 00:18:17,672
Phoon cuba dulu.

211
00:18:30,391 --> 00:18:31,522
Nah.

212
00:18:31,591 --> 00:18:32,696
Mama aku yang hantar untuk aku.

213
00:18:34,210 --> 00:18:37,765
Wah, fikir nak jumpa mama pun dah senyum lebar.

214
00:18:38,619 --> 00:18:40,008
Biar dia senyum sekali-sekala.

215
00:18:40,539 --> 00:18:42,924
- Betul.
- Ya.

216
00:18:43,031 --> 00:18:44,355
Tahniah, Maew.

217
00:18:44,595 --> 00:18:45,256
Mm.

218
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,631
Jadi, kat mana kau nak jumpa mama kau?

219
00:18:49,022 --> 00:18:51,896
Dia hantar alamat. Kami jumpa di sana.

220
00:18:52,085 --> 00:18:54,291
Di sana? Jepun?

221
00:18:54,589 --> 00:18:55,162
Ya.

222
00:18:55,717 --> 00:18:57,269
Wah.

223
00:18:57,620 --> 00:19:01,635
Jadi kau dan P'Fah dapat dating lagi di Jepun, kan?

224
00:19:01,730 --> 00:19:03,663
- Hei!
- Tak, tak!

225
00:19:03,783 --> 00:19:07,028
Ter, jangan usik dia. Tengok senyum tu—pipi dia mesti dah sakit.

226
00:19:07,779 --> 00:19:09,826
Alaa, malunya.

227
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:14,322
Aku cuma gembira. Apa salahnya?

228
00:19:16,591 --> 00:19:18,949
- Nah, ambil manisan ni.
- Terima kasih.

229
00:19:18,955 --> 00:19:20,503
Bagi-bagi snek!

230
00:19:20,527 --> 00:19:21,949
- Aku bagi kau dua.
- Terima kasih banyak.

231
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:25,348
- Nah.
- Hei, kenapa aku dapat satu je? Boleh dua?

232
00:19:25,355 --> 00:19:27,242
- Dia makan banyak.
- Kenapa?

233
00:19:27,324 --> 00:19:30,570
- Kau tak cukup hensem untuk dapat dua.
- Kalau macam tu, kau patut dapat satu je.

234
00:19:31,103 --> 00:19:32,094
- Hei!
- Lambat.

235
00:19:32,825 --> 00:19:34,118
Laju milik syaitan—jangan lawan aku.

236
00:19:34,197 --> 00:19:35,663
Kau asyik curi barang aku.

237
00:19:36,648 --> 00:19:37,954
Kali lepas pun kau tak bahagi bil.

238
00:19:38,528 --> 00:19:39,662
