490
00:40:54,536 --> 00:40:56,210
Jadi kau pun jenis macam tu sekarang?

491
00:40:56,231 --> 00:41:00,090
Fah, bila ada teman lelaki, sayang gila ya?

492
00:41:00,194 --> 00:41:01,882
- Kau tak ada pun.
- Hei.

493
00:41:01,933 --> 00:41:04,536
- Jaga mulut.
- Baguslah macam tu.

494
00:41:04,841 --> 00:41:06,471
- Kesian teman lelaki dia.
- Wow.

495
00:41:07,259 --> 00:41:09,887
Korang ni memang menyampah.

496
00:41:11,665 --> 00:41:13,080
Arthit merajuk ke?

497
00:41:15,998 --> 00:41:19,011
Wow, P'Fah bagi kamera sebagai hadiah?

498
00:41:19,272 --> 00:41:20,291
Ya.

499
00:41:20,362 --> 00:41:24,345
Itu besar. Hadiah aku dan Jo nampak kecil pula.

500
00:41:26,817 --> 00:41:27,640
Hadiah kau apa?

501
00:41:28,435 --> 00:41:29,077
Nah.

502
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:31,705
- Dari aku dan P'Hill.
- Terima kasih.

503
00:41:31,736 --> 00:41:32,908
Awak mesti suka.

504
00:41:33,931 --> 00:41:36,454
Korang ingat hari jadi aku pun aku dah gembira.

505
00:41:38,269 --> 00:41:40,285
Kalau kau betul-betul gembira, aku ambil balik.

506
00:41:40,311 --> 00:41:41,522
- Tak.
- Apa?

507
00:41:41,856 --> 00:41:42,558
Hei!

508
00:41:42,914 --> 00:41:43,920
Kau tarik kuat sangat.

509
00:41:44,499 --> 00:41:45,882
Kenapa kau lahir hari ni?

510
00:41:46,915 --> 00:41:48,122
Aku pun nak pergi sambut.

511
00:41:48,835 --> 00:41:51,194
Kalau macam tu batal rancangan keluarga, sambut dengan aku.

512
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:54,241
Oh, jadi kalau aku kena buang dari harta pusaka,

513
00:41:54,450 --> 00:41:55,468
kau nak tanggung aku?

514
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,662
Tak.

515
00:41:58,965 --> 00:41:59,957
Huh.

516
00:42:00,586 --> 00:42:02,656
Jom tengok hadiah hari jadi, aku dapat apa.

517
00:42:02,983 --> 00:42:03,751
Yang mana kita buka dulu?

518
00:42:06,469 --> 00:42:09,785
Yang aku last. Mula kotak muram tu dulu—nampak sedih elok.

519
00:42:09,814 --> 00:42:11,697
- Itu membuli.
- Tak apa.

520
00:42:11,724 --> 00:42:14,477
Membuli. Kau lebih-lebih.

521
00:42:14,511 --> 00:42:16,185
Itu gaya, tengoklah.

522
00:42:16,254 --> 00:42:17,808
Ringkas tapi nampak mahal.

523
00:42:18,013 --> 00:42:20,029
Atau mula dengan Dao?

524
00:42:20,746 --> 00:42:21,891
Kau belikan aku tangkal ke apa?

525
00:42:34,685 --> 00:42:35,720
Ambil gambar lagi?

526
00:42:37,208 --> 00:42:38,198
P'Fah, tengok.

527
00:42:39,322 --> 00:42:40,518
Awak nampak macam model.

528
00:42:43,222 --> 00:42:44,700
Sebab jurugambar dia hebat.

529
00:42:53,202 --> 00:42:54,685
Cepat betul masa berlalu, kan?

530
00:42:56,413 --> 00:42:58,684
Rasa macam baru je kita datang sini.

531
00:43:00,620 --> 00:43:01,413
Ya.

532
00:43:05,589 --> 00:43:06,650
Awak ingat tak, P'Fah?

533
00:43:07,057 --> 00:43:08,392
Awak pernah cakap...

534
00:43:08,921 --> 00:43:12,069
"Aku tak boleh jadi langit untuk sesiapa."

535
00:43:15,143 --> 00:43:16,081
Aku ingat.

536
00:43:16,728 --> 00:43:18,188
Sekarang awak masih rasa macam tu?

537
00:43:24,244 --> 00:43:25,490
Kalau itu yang Phoon nak,

538
00:43:25,826 --> 00:43:27,278
aku boleh jadi apa saja untuk awak.

539
00:43:31,665 --> 00:43:32,865
Terima kasih bawa aku ke sini.

540
00:43:34,690 --> 00:43:35,805
Terima kasih sekali lagi.

541
00:43:36,847 --> 00:43:38,077
Terima kasih banyak-banyak.

542
00:43:39,315 --> 00:43:41,385
Walaupun awak sibuk sangat,

543
00:43:42,441 --> 00:43:44,217
awak tetap luang masa dengan aku pada hari jadi aku.

544
00:43:48,117 --> 00:43:49,952
Aku tak buat banyak pun untuk awak, P'Fah.

545
00:43:52,454 --> 00:43:53,940
Jadi budak baik pun dah cukup, Phoon.

546
00:43:55,115 --> 00:43:56,223
Aku budak baik.

547
00:43:56,518 --> 00:43:59,352
- Dan bukan nakal.
- Awak nakal. Kucing nakal.

548
00:43:59,542 --> 00:44:01,340
Aku bukan nakal. Dan aku bukan kucing pun.

549
00:44:02,225 --> 00:44:03,208
Kenapa pula?

550
00:44:03,548 --> 00:44:05,400
Kawan-kawan awak pun panggil awak maew.

551
00:44:12,007 --> 00:44:13,383
- Maew.
- Ya?

552
00:44:15,622 --> 00:44:17,887
Nampak? Awak kata awak bukan kucing.

553
00:44:18,253 --> 00:44:19,314
Habis tu kenapa awak jawab?

554
00:44:22,628 --> 00:44:24,564
Kalau aku kucing,

555
00:44:25,512 --> 00:44:28,127
dan betul-betul ada sembilan nyawa,

556
00:44:29,767 --> 00:44:30,857
aku bagi semuanya pada awak, P'Fah.

557
00:44:31,075 --> 00:44:32,851
Hmm? Semua?

558
00:44:34,152 --> 00:44:35,121
Semua.

559
00:44:39,714 --> 00:44:40,882
Aku letak terus dalam tangan awak.

560
00:44:42,902 --> 00:44:43,848
Okey.

561
00:44:44,367 --> 00:44:46,207
Kalau macam tu, aku ambil semuanya.

562
00:44:53,794 --> 00:44:55,062
Selamat hari jadi.

563
00:44:56,524 --> 00:44:59,430
Terima kasih sebab jadi yang terbaik dalam hidup aku.

564
00:45:31,173 --> 00:45:33,191
Jom, cheers!

565
00:45:33,725 --> 00:45:34,797
Ya.

566
00:45:37,703 --> 00:45:39,011
Terima kasih datang, Dao.

567
00:45:40,017 --> 00:45:42,425
Hari jadi Maew—mana boleh aku tak datang?

568
00:45:43,567 --> 00:45:47,063
Ya, kalau kau tak datang hari jadi aku, tunggu nanti.

569
00:45:49,714 --> 00:45:50,816
Senang betul kau merajuk.

570
00:46:04,208 --> 00:46:05,979
Dah kosong—masa tambah lagi.

571
00:46:06,997 --> 00:46:08,020
Terus.

572
00:46:08,648 --> 00:46:09,720
Hei, Jo.

573
00:46:09,965 --> 00:46:11,149
Kawal teman lelaki kau.

574
00:46:11,220 --> 00:46:12,429
Hei, dia tengah seronok.

575
00:46:13,109 --> 00:46:14,949
- Kan?
- Ya.

576
00:46:18,974 --> 00:46:20,220
- North.
- Apa?

577
00:46:20,271 --> 00:46:21,380
Kau cuba buat aku mabuk ke?

578
00:46:22,059 --> 00:46:23,552
Mana ada.

579
00:46:24,222 --> 00:46:26,222
Macam mana kau kuat sangat minum?

580
00:46:26,586 --> 00:46:27,561
Mustahil.

581
00:46:27,749 --> 00:46:29,597
Jom kita tentukan.

582
00:46:30,511 --> 00:46:31,482
Siapa yang mabuk menang—

583
00:46:31,800 --> 00:46:33,437
tak, siapa mabuk dulu kalah.

584
00:46:33,450 --> 00:46:34,628
- Setuju.
- Ya.

585
00:46:35,296 --> 00:46:35,995
Jom.

586
00:46:36,149 --> 00:46:37,777
- Mari.
- Ya, mari.

587
00:46:37,816 --> 00:46:39,746
- Jom.
- Jom.

588
00:46:39,918 --> 00:46:43,854
Cheers. Habis satu.

589
00:46:49,091 --> 00:46:50,967
Aku paling sayang P'Hill.

590
00:46:53,260 --> 00:46:57,222
Muntah tak kira—tapi kalau pengsan, kau kalah.

591
00:46:58,872 --> 00:46:59,903
Cheers.

592
00:47:08,650 --> 00:47:11,826
Ya! Aku menang!

593
00:47:14,866 --> 00:47:15,761
Ya, sayang.

594
00:47:16,460 --> 00:47:17,315
Awak menang.

595
00:47:20,770 --> 00:47:21,496
Ish.

596
00:47:22,090 --> 00:47:24,182
Kenapa aku lahir jadi peti sejuk?

597
00:47:24,389 --> 00:47:26,271
Kalau ayam pun tak boleh disejukkan.

598
00:47:27,256 --> 00:47:28,434
Menyampah betul.

599
00:47:41,931 --> 00:47:44,160
Aku ambil tuala lap awak, ya?

600
00:47:46,920 --> 00:47:47,554
Tak nak.

601
00:47:50,561 --> 00:47:53,374
- Aku ambil tuala sekejap, Phoon.
- Tak nak.

602
00:47:54,395 --> 00:47:57,644
Walau sebaik mana orang yang awak jumpa,

603
00:47:58,429 --> 00:48:00,189
jangan tinggalkan aku, ya?

604
00:48:04,143 --> 00:48:05,595
Apa awak merepek ni, Phoon?

605
00:48:05,979 --> 00:48:07,379
Tak tahu. Aku mabuk.

606
00:48:22,139 --> 00:48:22,958
P’Mhor.

607
00:48:23,379 --> 00:48:24,502
P’Mhor Fah.

608
00:48:24,608 --> 00:48:25,204
Ya?

609
00:48:27,299 --> 00:48:28,450
Jangan sampai aku tahu, ya?

610
00:48:30,275 --> 00:48:31,192
Tahu pasal apa?

611
00:48:31,800 --> 00:48:36,607
Yang awak curi-curi tengok orang lain masa kelas.

612
00:48:38,521 --> 00:48:39,272
Betul ke?

613
00:48:44,379 --> 00:48:45,505
P’Fah, awak suka budak tak?

614
00:48:46,789 --> 00:48:47,792
Budak?

615
00:48:49,742 --> 00:48:51,722
Ya, aku suka.

616
00:48:52,404 --> 00:48:53,103
Kenapa?

617
00:48:54,728 --> 00:48:56,758
Aku pun suka budak.

618
00:48:57,244 --> 00:48:58,970
Aku nak ada anak.

619
00:48:59,620 --> 00:49:00,654
Satu rumah penuh anak.

620
00:49:01,780 --> 00:49:07,211
Tapi P’Fah mungkin tak ada masa untuk anak-anak.

621
00:49:07,752 --> 00:49:09,829
Lagipun mereka akan sayang aku lebih dari awak.

622
00:49:12,180 --> 00:49:15,183
Aku jadi Papa.

623
00:49:15,662 --> 00:49:17,435
Papa yang paling faham anak-anak.

624
00:49:25,151 --> 00:49:26,888
Kenapa P’Fah tak jawab?

625
00:49:28,179 --> 00:49:28,911
Err...

626
00:49:29,438 --> 00:49:31,074
Awak tak tanya apa-apa pun, Phoon.

627
00:49:33,416 --> 00:49:36,309
Jadi P’Fah nak namakan anak kita apa?

628
00:49:37,592 --> 00:49:38,814
Nama?

629
00:49:42,934 --> 00:49:44,361
Patut nama apa?

630
00:49:46,445 --> 00:49:48,611
Tak tahu. Awak tentukanlah, Phoon.

631
00:49:49,902 --> 00:49:51,712
Tapi P’Fah kerja kuat sangat.

632
00:49:52,668 --> 00:49:56,835
P’Fah sempat ke untuk aku dan anak-anak?

633
00:49:59,822 --> 00:50:04,148
Jangan risau, Phoon. Aku cuba luang masa untuk awak dan anak-anak.

634
00:50:04,434 --> 00:50:08,562
Kalau macam tu, P’Fah kena jadi Papa yang penyayang.

635
00:50:09,337 --> 00:50:10,211
Aku akan.

636
00:50:10,592 --> 00:50:11,645
Tapi sekarang,

637
00:50:12,693 --> 00:50:13,797
dah lewat.

638
00:50:14,242 --> 00:50:15,161
Jom tidur, ya?

639
00:50:15,367 --> 00:50:17,798
Tak. Aku tak nak tidur. Aku tak mengantuk.

640
00:50:17,884 --> 00:50:19,870
- Tapi awak mabuk, Phoon.
- Taklah.

641
00:50:20,551 --> 00:50:22,263
Kenapa Papa bergaduh dengan aku?

642
00:50:22,976 --> 00:50:23,714
Tunggu sekejap...

643
00:50:24,354 --> 00:50:25,616
"Papa"?

644
00:50:25,909 --> 00:50:27,505
Papa bergaduh dengan aku.

645
00:50:28,725 --> 00:50:31,160
Phoon, jangan nakal.

646
00:50:33,114 --> 00:50:36,557
Papa marah aku—Papa marah budak juga?

647
00:50:37,820 --> 00:50:39,616
Kalau mereka nakal, kenalah.

648
00:50:39,660 --> 00:50:41,050
Tak, jangan marah mereka.

649
00:50:41,457 --> 00:50:44,480
Kalau Papa marah, aku bawa mereka lari.

650
00:50:44,768 --> 00:50:46,019
Aku tak bagi mereka jumpa Papa.

651
00:50:51,460 --> 00:50:52,361
Kalau macam tu...

652
00:50:53,524 --> 00:50:55,245
Mama, jangan kejam sangat dengan Papa, ya?

653
00:51:01,952 --> 00:51:04,285
Aduh, sakit sini.

654
00:51:04,548 --> 00:51:05,767
Sakit sini.

655
00:51:19,570 --> 00:51:21,220
Sini pun sakit.

656
00:51:33,937 --> 00:51:34,681
Selamat malam.

657
00:51:47,709 --> 00:51:48,471
Nah, Phoon.

658
00:51:49,005 --> 00:51:49,804
Hati-hati, panas.

659
00:52:03,293 --> 00:52:04,253
Awak sakit kepala?

660
00:52:06,321 --> 00:52:08,517
Sikit.

661
00:52:08,709 --> 00:52:09,666
Lain kali,

662
00:52:10,038 --> 00:52:11,677
jangan minum banyak sangat, ya?

663
00:52:15,848 --> 00:52:16,324
Mm.

664
00:52:17,426 --> 00:52:19,480
Sedap. P’Fah buat sendiri ke?

665
00:52:19,912 --> 00:52:20,708
Ya.

666
00:52:21,309 --> 00:52:22,213
Kalau awak suka,

667
00:52:22,408 --> 00:52:23,263
makan banyak, ya?

668
00:52:31,674 --> 00:52:32,456
Phoon.

669
00:52:33,931 --> 00:52:35,422
Awak ingat tak apa yang awak cakap

670
00:52:35,816 --> 00:52:37,062
malam tadi?

671
00:52:38,124 --> 00:52:39,245
Malam tadi?

672
00:52:40,088 --> 00:52:41,062
Kenapa?

673
00:52:42,302 --> 00:52:44,478
Awak ada cakap pasal

674
00:52:45,394 --> 00:52:46,282
nak ada anak.

675
00:52:50,637 --> 00:52:51,631
Anak?

676
00:52:51,893 --> 00:52:52,570
Ya.

677
00:52:53,543 --> 00:52:56,837
Awak tanya, "P’Fah suka budak tak?"

678
00:52:56,942 --> 00:52:58,896
"P’Fah nak ada anak tak?"

679
00:53:02,078 --> 00:53:06,268
Oh... mesti aku mabuk malam tadi.

680
00:53:06,537 --> 00:53:07,508
Aku merepek je.

681
00:53:16,423 --> 00:53:18,226
Aku tak nak minum lagi.

682
00:53:19,521 --> 00:53:20,600
Kenapa pula?

683
00:53:22,386 --> 00:53:26,122
Aku rasa awak comel bila mabuk.

684
00:53:29,533 --> 00:53:33,182
Tapi tadi awak kata jangan minum banyak.

685
00:53:35,764 --> 00:53:36,737
Betul juga.

686
00:53:38,010 --> 00:53:42,293
Maksud aku, awak boleh minum—tapi bila aku ada.

687
00:53:51,355 --> 00:53:52,608
Makan banyak, ya?

688
00:53:53,162 --> 00:53:54,327
- Mama.
- Hmm?

689
00:53:58,217 --> 00:54:02,041
Kalau Mama lapar lagi, Papa boleh buat lagi.

690
00:54:07,613 --> 00:54:08,739
Daotok.

691
00:54:10,157 --> 00:54:15,162
Kalau asyik tenung kami, aku muntah atas kau nanti.

692
00:54:17,277 --> 00:54:18,440
Jangan cakap pasal muntah.

693
00:54:18,887 --> 00:54:22,834
Dah. Berhenti gaduh, tolong aku semak keputusan.

694
00:54:22,986 --> 00:54:24,497
Mari, tolong bagi semangat.

695
00:54:26,300 --> 00:54:27,182
Bangun.

696
00:54:31,840 --> 00:54:34,025
PENGUMUMAN KEPUTUSAN PEPERIKSAAN
FAKULTI SENI HALUS, IJAZAH SARJANA MUDA, FOTOGRAFI KREATIF
TEERAPAT CHAOWAKORNKUL

697
00:54:36,174 --> 00:54:36,906
Sial.

698
00:54:43,823 --> 00:54:44,937
Tak apa, bro.

699
00:54:46,568 --> 00:54:48,540
Kalau tak dapat tahun ni, aku cuba lagi tahun depan.

700
00:54:51,285 --> 00:54:53,146
Kau dapat—sial, kau memang dapat!

701
00:54:53,191 --> 00:54:56,137
Nama kau ada. Mari tengok.

702
00:54:56,949 --> 00:54:58,960
UNIVERSITI THIRASOPHON UMUM KEPUTUSAN KEMASUKAN PILIHAN PROGRAM NO. 6
TEERAPAT CHAOWAKORNKUL

703
00:55:00,468 --> 00:55:01,875
- Aku dapat!
- Ya.

704
00:55:02,133 --> 00:55:04,957
Ya!

705
00:55:55,525 --> 00:55:59,952
Langit tak pernah sama tiap hari, tapi tetap memukau.

706
00:56:23,066 --> 00:56:26,001
Untuk Typhoon,

707
00:56:31,293 --> 00:56:34,832
Walaupun aku dah tulis tak terkira surat,

708
00:56:37,168 --> 00:56:39,810
untuk ramai orang,

709
00:56:42,157 --> 00:56:46,011
ini mungkin kali pertama aku tulis untuk diri sendiri.

710
00:57:28,428 --> 00:57:29,454
Terima kasih.

711
00:57:45,589 --> 00:57:47,600
Terima kasih sebab jadi lebih kuat,

712
00:57:50,007 --> 00:57:52,297
dan terima sakit yang kau tanggung.

713
00:57:59,934 --> 00:58:02,149
Terima kasih sebab akhirnya jumpa diri sendiri.

714
00:58:03,622 --> 00:58:08,358
Terima kasih sebab berani buka hati, dan jumpa ramai orang baik.

715
00:58:08,474 --> 00:58:09,503
Hei, kau.

716
00:58:09,786 --> 00:58:10,877
Kelas kat sini.

717
00:58:12,801 --> 00:58:13,946
Ya, aku dalam fakulti.

718
00:58:14,493 --> 00:58:17,274
Macam mana ni? Phoon sesat macam biasa lagi.

719
00:58:17,848 --> 00:58:19,345
Dia boleh hidup tanpa kita ke?

720
00:58:23,213 --> 00:58:26,591
Kelas dah habis? Aku datang ambil awak.

721
00:58:29,939 --> 00:58:31,222
Tak payah.

722
00:58:32,831 --> 00:58:33,945
Kenapa?

723
00:58:37,770 --> 00:58:43,788
Terima kasih sebab percaya pada cinta, sampai sedar kau mampu sayang sedalam itu.

724
00:58:50,100 --> 00:58:52,312
- Lepas ni ke mana?
- Mungkin pergi makan.

725
00:58:52,797 --> 00:58:53,280
Awak pula?

726
00:58:53,760 --> 00:58:54,499
Tak tahu.

727
00:58:55,232 --> 00:58:55,979
Saya pun lapar.

728
00:58:56,961 --> 00:58:57,893
Tapi saya tak rasa nak makan dengan awak.

729
00:58:58,509 --> 00:58:59,472
Kenapa dengan awak?

730
00:59:00,848 --> 00:59:02,010
Phoon tak bagi saya pergi jemput dia.

731
00:59:06,280 --> 00:59:09,946
Atau dia tengah belajar fotografi, ramai orang keliling.

732
00:59:09,964 --> 00:59:11,361
- Ya, mungkin.
- Macam Hill cakap.

733
00:59:15,192 --> 00:59:18,367
Oh, kesiannya awak, P'Fah.

734
00:59:18,962 --> 00:59:20,571
Hidup awak tragis sangat.

735
00:59:21,288 --> 00:59:24,560
Jangan sangat dengar cakap si dungu tu.
Awak tahu Phoon sayang awak mati-mati.

736
00:59:24,717 --> 00:59:25,321
Saya tahu.

737
00:59:25,737 --> 00:59:27,162
Saya pun tak percaya sepatah pun cakap mereka.

738
00:59:27,296 --> 00:59:29,170
Hah?

739
00:59:30,331 --> 00:59:32,382
- Hei, Jo, awak dengar tak?
- Ya.

740
00:59:32,500 --> 00:59:34,241
- Jumpa di kedai P'Gib.
- Apa hal?

741
00:59:34,256 --> 00:59:34,986
Dia makin berani sekarang.

742
00:59:35,777 --> 00:59:36,890
Asyik senyum je.

743
00:59:41,657 --> 00:59:42,562
Mana Phoon?

744
00:59:45,614 --> 00:59:46,423
Di sini.

745
01:00:06,444 --> 01:00:10,253
Kalau tak menyusahkan, boleh jumpa lagi?

746
01:00:10,946 --> 01:00:13,122
Ada hal penting saya nak cakap dengan awak.

747
01:00:14,407 --> 01:00:16,082
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

748
01:00:27,016 --> 01:00:28,266
Kenapa, sayang?

749
01:00:41,555 --> 01:00:42,558
Hai.

750
01:00:46,533 --> 01:00:47,373
Hai.

751
01:00:49,685 --> 01:00:51,462
Terima kasih sebab sudi jumpa saya.

752
01:00:54,441 --> 01:00:56,134
Terima kasih juga sebab sudi datang jumpa saya.

753
01:00:59,546 --> 01:01:05,146
Pernah terfikir tak apa awak buat kalau dulu saya pergi?

754
01:01:08,805 --> 01:01:13,321
Macam saya cakap dulu, saya akan balik ke tempat sama—tempat kita selesa.

755
01:01:13,685 --> 01:01:15,075
Tak kisah berapa lama pun.

756
01:01:23,777 --> 01:01:25,989
Walau lama mana pun, awak tetap tunggu?

757
01:01:28,223 --> 01:01:28,980
Ya.

758
01:01:34,997 --> 01:01:35,823
Setahun.

759
01:01:37,130 --> 01:01:37,783
Tak apa.

760
01:01:42,617 --> 01:01:43,662
Dua tahun.

761
01:01:44,250 --> 01:01:45,032
Itu pun tak apa.

762
01:01:45,580 --> 01:01:46,829
Lima tahun.

763
01:01:47,654 --> 01:01:48,407
Itu pun tak apa juga.

764
01:01:48,635 --> 01:01:49,730
Kalau sepuluh tahun pula.

765
01:01:50,801 --> 01:01:52,841
Phoon, berhenti usik saya dah.

766
01:01:56,419 --> 01:01:57,826
Saya nak mula kira undur.

767
01:01:58,432 --> 01:02:01,468
Kalau awak masih diam, awak kena denda.

768
01:02:02,823 --> 01:02:03,656
Sepuluh.

769
01:02:04,311 --> 01:02:05,034
Sembilan.

770
01:02:05,663 --> 01:02:06,337
Lapan.

771
01:02:07,082 --> 01:02:07,681
Tujuh.

772
01:02:08,565 --> 01:02:09,050
Enam.

773
01:02:10,059 --> 01:02:10,909
Lima.

774
01:02:11,666 --> 01:02:12,687
- Empat.
- P'Fah.

775
01:02:12,733 --> 01:02:14,334
- P'Fah.
- Tiga.

776
01:02:14,364 --> 01:02:15,365
Saya cuma—

777
01:02:15,463 --> 01:02:16,706
- Dua.
- nak buat awak terkejut je, itu saja.

778
01:02:17,025 --> 01:02:17,957
Satu.

779
01:02:18,272 --> 01:02:19,114
P'…

780
01:02:43,505 --> 01:02:44,820
Saya sayang awak, P'Fah.

781
01:02:46,882 --> 01:02:48,394
Saya pun sayang awak, Phoon.

